    How to launch my Shinyapp

    app.Rmd
    library(phyllispkg)

    There are three data set use in this package and all are provided by the Johns Hopkins University Center for Systems Science and Engineering (JHU CSSE) and Rami Krispin and other 4 contributor provided a tidy format of the data as r package coronavirus. The package provides the map dataset, which contains longitude and latitude of 10 main countries Australia, Belgium, China, Germany, India, Italy, Japan, Spain, United Kingdom and US and different type of cases number every day.

    It can be accessed via:

    library(tibble)
library(phyllispkg)
map
